---
import { Carousel3D } from '@/components/Carousel3D/Carousel3D';
import LayoutClean from '@/layouts/LayoutClean.astro';
import {Back} from "../../components/Back/Back"
---

<LayoutClean title="Pilsen Digital">
	<main class="w-full flex justify-center items-center flex-col mt-10">
		<div class="w-[90vw]">
			<div class="flex gap-2 items-end flex-wrap">
				<Back client:only />
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-6xl">Pilsen Digital</h2>
				<h4 class="text-gray-500 text-3xl md:text-4xl">(March 2022 - Aug 2022)</h4>
			</div>
			<div class="containerCarousel3D flex justify-center my-10">
				<Carousel3D client:only imgs={[
				"/assets/pilsen/pilsen1.jpg",
				"/assets/pilsen/pilsen2.jpg",
				"/assets/pilsen/pilsen3.jpg",
				"/assets/pilsen/pilsen4.jpg",
				"/assets/pilsen/pilsen5.jpg",
				]} web='https://drive.google.com/file/d/1P-cQtRLeUMFPhQw9oOxvGOZo7kNgPOCm/view?usp=sharing' github='https://github.com/frandepe/pilsen-sp'/>	
			</div>
			<div class="text-white-100">
				<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 my-10">
				  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Frontend Developer at Pilsen Digital</h1>
			  
				  <div class="mb-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Responsibilities and Achievements:</h2>
					
					<div class="mb-4">
					  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Client Communication and Implementation:</h3>
					  <p>I worked for a company based in CÃ³rdoba, Argentina, called Pilsen Digital. I was responsible for the frontend development using React. My main task was to implement client ideas communicated by my manager. We had weekly meetings where my manager conveyed the project requirements, and I also maintained communication with the backend team.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="mb-4">
					  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Metal Factory Web Application:</h3>
					  <p>The web application was for a metal factory and required a dashboard for employees to track their activities. The most important feature was a drag-and-drop system for employees to manage their workflow. This system allowed them to visualize and organize their processes efficiently.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="mb-4">
					  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">WordPress Modifications:</h3>
					  <p>Besides the main project, I also worked on modifying an existing WordPress site, ensuring it met the client's needs and enhanced user experience.</p>
					</div>
				  </div>
			  
				  <div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Key Features and Functionalities:</h2>
					
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
					  <li>React for frontend development.</li>
					  <li>Weekly meetings to understand and implement client requirements.</li>
					  <li>Collaboration with the backend team for seamless integration.</li>
					  <li>Development of a drag-and-drop system for employee activity management.</li>
					  <li>Modifications to an existing WordPress site.</li>
					</ul>
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			  
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-10">
			<h3 class="text-4xl my-10">Technologies used</h3>
			<div class="flex justify-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-items-center items-center">
					<img src="/imgs/icons/react.png" width={40}/> <p>React</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-items-center items-center">
					<img src="/imgs/icons/React Bootstrap.png" width={40}/> <p>Bootstrap</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-items-center items-center">
					<img src="/imgs/icons/Redux.png" width={40}/> <p>Redux</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-items-center items-center">
					<img src="/imgs/icons/WordPress.png" width={40}/> <p>WordPress</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-items-center items-center">
					<img src="/imgs/icons/Postman.png" width={40}/> <p>Postman</p>
				</div>
				
			</div>
			
		</div>
	</main>
</LayoutClean>